        <strong style="font-size:0.95rem;">Circumference Calculator</strong>
        <p style="opacity:0.6;font-size:0.83rem;margin:0.4rem 0 0;line-height:1.4;">Calculate the circumference, area, and diameter of any circle instantly. Understand the math behind C = 2πr with our int...</p>
      </a>
